==Arabic==
===Etymology===
Arabic {{ARchar|[[نسخ]]}} (''naskh'', transcription) + {{ARchar|[[تعليق]]}} (''ta‘líq'', oblique hanging [[ductus]] style of calligraphy).

===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|نستعليق}}''' (nastaʕlíq)

# [[Nastaliq]], [[nastaleeq]]: A style of [[Arabic]] [[calligraphy]] or [[font]], most popular for the [[Urdu]] language.

